videos.headline: Virginia defense setting tone early
videos.description: Cavaliers' CB Quin Blanding intercepts Daniel Jones and returns it 58 yards for the score.

videos.headline: Duke defense ties the game
videos.description: Blue Devils' CB Jeremy McDuffie snags an interception from Kurt Benkert and races for a 42-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Duke QB makes big throw for TD
videos.description: Daniel Jones completes the pass in a tight window to TE Davis Koppenhaver for a 7-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Virginia scores TD right before half
videos.description: QB Kurt Benkert throws a short pass to Olamide Zaccheaus  and he does the rest for the 11-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Virginia scores controversial TD
videos.description: QB Benkert delivers a pass to Doni Dowling  for a 5-yard score. (It would be reviewed and ruled a touchdown)

videos.headline: Duke making plays on special teams
videos.description: Shaun Wilson returns a kick for 76 yards to give the Blue Devils great field position.

videos.headline: Duke cuts lead with TD
videos.description: QB Quentin Harris keeps it himself and runs it in for a 4-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Virginia defense big in the clutch
videos.description: Cavaliers' CB Charles Snowden comes barreling in to sack Daniel Jones on a critical third down.

videos.headline: Cavaliers' defense wins the game
videos.description: Daniel Jones attempts to heave a pass to T.J. Rahming on fourth down but CB Juan Thornhill is there to break it up.
